title: BREAKING: Man injured by 'flying debris' at Victoria Station as Storm Doris wreaks havoc
text:
DS INCIDENT: A man has been hit by flying debris outside Victoria Station 
Emergency services have scambled to the scene to reports of an injured man outside the central London station. 
The condition of the man is not yet known. 
It comes after Storm Doris claimed its first victim after a woman was killed by a flying peice of debris in Wolverhampton. 
MORE TO FOLLOW
